## About The Project

![Landing Screen Shot][landing-screenshot]
<br/>
Ticket generator is basically a poc project to see how to deal with datetimes
and timezones

The 2 principles of project:

- Clean templating for future projects
- Follow react principles as long as you can

<!-- GETTING STARTED -->

## Getting Started

### Prerequisites

- Node.js v18.0 or upper
- Npm

### Installation

1. Clone the repo
   ```sh
   git clone https://github.com/onuraltuntasb/ticket-generator-ui
   ```
2. Install NPM packages
   ```sh
   npm install
   ```
3. Run feelsafe-backend from https://github.com/onuraltuntasb/feelsafe-backend
   ```js
    mvn spring-boot:run
   ```
